flowchart LR
    U[User/Device] --> ID[Identity + Device Posture]
    ID --> G[Gateway]
    G --> S1[Service A]
    S1 --> S2[Service B]
    S2 --> D[(Data Store)]

    WI[Workload Identity + mTLS] --> S1
    WI --> S2
    PDP[Central Policy Decision] --> S1
    PDP --> S2
    PEP[Local Policy Enforcement] --> S1
    PEP --> S2
    EX[Exception Registry with TTL] --> PDP

    NOTE1[No implicit trust by network location]
    NOTE2[Every hop re-evaluates identity and policy]

    WI -.-> NOTE1
    PDP -.-> NOTE2
